import React from 'react'
import {DownloadSection,
        DownloadContainer,
        DownloadTitle,
        DownloadIcon,
        DownloadBtnLink,
        DownloadBtn} from './DownloadElements'

function index() {
    return (
        <DownloadSection>
            <DownloadContainer>
                <DownloadTitle>Download Croco-OS:</DownloadTitle>
                <DownloadIcon>
                    <DownloadBtnLink>
                        <DownloadBtn>
                            Download
                        </DownloadBtn>
                    </DownloadBtnLink>
                </DownloadIcon>
            </DownloadContainer>
        </DownloadSection>
    )
}

export default index
